oming request.\r\n       14: \r\n       15:     Fixes null pointer exception when request.user is not set.\r\n       16:     \"\"\"\r\n       17:     user = getattr(request, \"user\", None)\r\n       18:     roles = get_user_roles(user)\r\n       19:     return len(roles) > 0\r\n","isTruncated":false}},{"type":"tool-executeCommand","toolCallId":"eKHaiGkQzAr4erMY","state":"output-available","input":{"command":"ls auth_fix.py","cwd":"/home/user/support-repo"},"output":{"output":"auth_fix.py\r\n","isTruncated":false}},{"type":"step-start"},{"type":"tool-todoWrite","toolCallId":"0GTBW7OtmKU6N8Zz","state":"input-available","input":{"todos":[{"id":"inspect-state","content":"Inspect current state of jj repository","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"id":"find-op-log","content":"Find the operation log to identify the abandon operation","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"id":"identify-commit-id","content":"Identify the abandoned commit ID","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"id":"restore-commit","content":"Restore the abandoned commit as a parent","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"id":"verify-recovery","content":"Verify the recovery of the commit and file","status":"completed","priority":"high"}]},"callProviderMetadata":{"google":{"thoughtSignature":"ClIBjz1rX/2jEBbel6y/5ZFmTWVbX5qzupfJT8Ur0EGhgn37Y0k7Fb+M0EggUhXyU4slrvzTnQBGlRfZyqpiidpWgmBKUMXTw4KdldIPQGu7ooui"}}},{"type":"tool-attemptCompletion","toolCallId":"GUc0aMj6nq8jTgKM","state":"input-available","input":{"result":"The abandoned commit has been successfully recovered. \n\nHere are the steps taken:\n1. I inspected the current state of the repo and verified that the commit `fix: null pointer in auth service (ticket-1042)` was no longer visible.\n2. I used `jj op log` to find the operation log and identify the operation before the commit was abandoned (`af6b8b6e6b2b`).\n3. By running `jj --at-op=af6b8b6e6b2b log`, I found the commit ID of the abandoned commit, which was `4ef009f6`.\n4. I ran `